data.description: $273,500 of loan is assumable at 2.375%! Welcome to your Sylvan Lake retreat resting on 2.55 private acres with 264 feet of lakeshore with sandy bottom and great fishing! As soon as you pull in the driveway you will be in love! This 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home includes a 4 car 45'x26' garage for all the toys!  Another 22x16' bunkhouse/gameroom or use as a heated shop area!  Home features modern cabinets, a master suite w/ wood burning fireplace, another wood burning fireplace in the huge lower level family room!  Tons of space for friends and family to enjoy.  The front yard comes completely fenced and also features plum and apple trees!  Furnishings are negotiable to make it ready to go for your summer fun!  Start making lake memories today!
